entries.title_d: Destroy the Corsair Pirates and recover the cargo
entries.title: Lok System: Destroy the Corsair Pirates
entries.quest_target_d: This craft has the cargo, you must destroy them before they can Hyperspace Jump away
entries.quest_location_d: Corsair Lane in the Lok System
entries.quest_escort_d: A dangerous escort, destroy these to protect the cargo.
entries.failed_escape: You let him get away, this is unacceptable.
